com.paydiant.android.core.domain

Class Payment

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.paydiant.android.core.domain.Payment
  • Deprecated. 
    As of 6.5.0.3.a. See ITransactionManagerFacade.makePayment(Payment)

    @Deprecated
public class Payment
extends Object
    The Class Payment. The Payment object which serves as the request object when creating a payment transaction. For ease of the Mobile SDK client a separate Payment object has been used to encapsulate the request information instead of re using the PaymentTransaction object.
    Author:
    Paydiant Inc.
